# Tooling and dependencies (reference only)
# Python dependencies:
#   pip install -r requirements.txt
#
# External tools (optional):
#   - radare2 (static analysis / disassembly)
#   - gdb (dynamic tracing, MI2 — Linux only)
#   - Ghidra (headless decompiler for pseudocode)
#
# AI dependencies (optional — graceful fallback to classical):
#   - openai / anthropic / mistralai (LLM providers)
#   - torch + torch-geometric (GNN embeddings)
#   - Ollama (local LLM inference)
#
# Optional helpers:
#   - pygdbmi (already in requirements.txt)
#   - r2pipe (already in requirements.txt)
